=== Etymology ===
Named after ''[[w:Alois Alzheimer|Alois Alzheimer]]'' (June 14, 1864 - December 19, 1915), a German neurologist who described the disease in 1906.

===Noun===
'''Alzheimer's Disease'''

# A disorder of loss mental functions resulting from brain tissue changes, and the causes are yet to be fully elucidated.  Senile dementia of Alzheimer's type.

